tart":117.39,"time_end":120.68},{"position":48,"content":"Good. I'd like to do that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/48.mp3","time_start":120.78,"time_end":123.01},{"position":49,"content":"Does this trip also go into the desert?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/49.mp3","time_start":123.01,"time_end":125.65},{"position":50,"content":"No, it continues to Santa Monica where most people like to stop and do some shopping.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/50.mp3","time_start":125.65,"time_end":130.41},{"position":51,"content":"We have enough of that at home so that doesn't interest us.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/51.mp3","time_start":130.67,"time_end":134.61},{"position":52,"content":"OK. Well you could go straight on to San Diego.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/52.mp3","time_start":134.61,"time_end":138.19},{"position":53,"content":"That's good for beaches isn't it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/53.mp3","time_start":138.31,"time_end":140.48},{"position":54,"content":"That's right, that's a good place to relax and your children might like to visit the zoo before flying home.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/54.mp3","time_start":140.48,"time_end":146.36},{"position":55,"content":"I don't think so.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/55.mp3","time_start":146.48,"time_end":148.09},{"position":56,"content":"We want some time for sunbathing and swimming.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/56.mp3","time_start":148.18,"time_end":151.22},{"position":57,"content":"So how many days are the trips and how much do they cost?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/57.mp3","time_start":151.91,"time_end":155.79},{"position":58,"content":"The first one I told you about is a self-drive tour through California","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/58.mp3","time_start":155.79,"time_end":160.43},{"position":59,"content":"which lasts twelve days and covers 2,020 kilometres.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/59.mp3","time_start":160.43,"time_end":165.19},{"position":60,"content":"The shortest journey is 206 kilometres","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/60.mp3","time_start":165.59,"time_end":168.92},{"position":61,"content":"and the longest is 632 kilometres.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/61.mp3","time_start":168.92,"time_end":172.23},{"position":62,"content":"The cost is £525 per person.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/62.mp3","time_start":172.48,"time_end":176.06},{"position":63,"content":"That includes accommodation, car rental and a flight but no meals.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-1-part-1-2023-06-09-21-53-29/63.mp3","time_start":176.06,"time_end":180.71},{"position":64,"content":"OK. And the other trip?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-lis